# Defensive .gitignore at the eq-intake root.
#
# This directory is currently the EQ Phase 1 build bundle (docs + source
# staging + the eq-platform monorepo). If you `git init` here later, this
# file makes sure secrets and build junk don't accidentally land in a
# commit before you've thought about a proper .gitignore.

# Secrets — never commit any of these
key.txt
*.key
*.pem
.env
.env.local
.env.*
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*

# Dependencies + build output
node_modules/
**/node_modules/
dist/
**/dist/
.pnpm-store/
**/src/generated/

# Editor / OS
.DS_Store
.vscode/
.idea/

# Logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# Real customer data — SimPRO exports + derived rollups.
# Contains live Equinix/NEXTDC/etc. contacts (names, emails, mobile numbers,
# ABNs). Must not land on any remote, even a private one.
simpro/
demos/simpro-customer-rollup/customer-rollup.csv
demos/simpro-customer-rollup/eq-quotes-by-site.csv

# Overnight review reports + ephemeral working files
OVERNIGHT-REVIEW-*.md
**/fuzz-overnight*.mjs

# Claude session tooling
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

